Diamond Bank of Nigeria Sells ADIC Insurance Holding to NSIA Participation

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-19T11:47:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/diamond-bank-of-nigeria-sells-adic-insurance-holding-to-nsia-participation.html
Diamond Bank Plc (DIAMONDB)  said it sold its
96.15 percent stake in ADIC Insurance Ltd. to NSIA
Participations SA Holding as part of a strategy to exit
businesses outside of banking.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  